Titolo: Joe Dever's Lone Wolf

Anno: 2013

Descrizione: Joe Dever's Lone Wolf is a role-playing game video game developed by Italian studio Forge Reply and published by Bulkypix for iOS on October 29, 2013, and is now also available on Android. It is based on the series of gamebooks by author Joe Dever entitled Lone Wolf. The story involves Lone Wolf adventuring to uncover the secret of the Shianti Cube.